    "ConclusionsChatGPT is an AI model which is already used by millions of users.",
    "This article highlights the possible opportunities and challenges that could arise due to the innovation of ChatGPT in academia.",
    "Although the challenges of ChatGPT include inaccuracy, fairness, ethical issues, and the like, these can be addressed by improving the effectiveness and responsible usage of this language model.",
    "Again, the conversations with every user are stored and used further to learn the model (ChatGPT) for improving its accuracy to provide better user support.",
    "So, for the time being, the opportunities of ChatGPT will increase while the problems raised due to ChatGPT will decrease."
